# Complexity
- Time complexity: $$O(n^2)$$
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

- Space complexity: $$O(n^2)$$
<!-- Add your space complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

# Code
```
class Solution {
  public int[][] generateMatrix(int n) {
    int x = 0, y = -1, cnt = 1;
    var xMoves = new int[] {n};
    var yMoves = new int[] {n+1};
    var mat = new int[n][n];

    for (var d = 0; cnt <= n*n; d = (d+1) % 4) {
      var moves = d % 2 == 0 ? yMoves : xMoves;
      moves[0]--;

      for (var i = 0; i < moves[0]; i++) {
        switch(d) {
          case 0 : y++; break;
          case 1 : x++; break;
          case 2 : y--; break;
          case 3 : x--; break;
        }
        mat[x][y] = cnt++;
      }
    }
    return mat;
  }
}
```
