RESULT: ([5,0], [5], [0])


A = -3, curr_sum = 4, curr_sum%K = 4 map now is: 0-->1, 4-->4, 2-->1 So this means we found a remainder that was already there! count+=3 RESULT: ([5,0], [5], [0], [5,0,-2,-3], [0,-2,-3], [-2,-3]) (added three more)


