# Prefix Sum: 
    Prefix Sum = The Running Sum of an array.
    The sum b/w any 2 elements  = PS[j]-PS[i-1]
    for ex: j = 4, i = 2
    [0,-2,-3] = 4-9 = 5


# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
Store the mod of PS in a hashmap.
PS = PS%k
At any given point ans +=hashMap.get(PS);

