Keep track of count of subarrays till index i whose sum % k = {0,1,..,k-1}. Add that count to answer when sum % k = 0.

# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
For keeping track of count of sum % k, we can use a hashmap.

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
